* version 0.1.2 = tested with mapbox-gl-js v0.36.0
* version 0.2.0 = tested with mapbox-gl-js v0.43.0
* version 0.4.0 = tested with mapbox-gl-js v1.1.0
* version 0.5.0 = tested with mapbox-gl-js v1.4.0


🚦Limitations🚦
